title: Eskimo Brothers ( Ray J and Bow-wow interview)
itunes:title: Eskimo Brothers ( Ray J and Bow-wow interview)
description:
Today on the show they had a pop up pull up from random duo Ray J and Bow- Wow. During the interview they shared funny experiences that happend while they traveled together, and while Bow-Wow spoke about having a hard time leaving the single life, Ray J did not want any parts in it he just wanted to keep the peace and promote his Raycons and fitness belt. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the police officer who caused a pregnant woman to get into a crash and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
